title: You Are Blessed And Cannot Be Cursed | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: You Are Blessed And Cannot Be Cursed | Joel Osteen
description:
Before anyone could speak anything negative over your life, God put a blessing on you. Once you understand who you are and what God has already done, you'll realize that nothing can stop you from fulfilling your God-given destiny. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
